1. Get the instance-id
2. Query the instance-id

public Ip query
aws ec2 describe-instances --instance-ids i-05493202d91f9ab56 --query 'Reservations[0].Instances[0].PublicIpAddress' --output text

private ip query
aws ec2 describe-instances --instance-ids i-05493202d91f9ab56 --query 'Reservations[0].Instances[0].PrivateIpAddress' --output text

